{"tid":2254037,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"你的網站密碼會如何外洩？如何兼顧方便和安全？","createTime":"2020-10-22T14:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T06:45:53.000Z","uid":175208,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6e8326e4279f713d44ce5852634231c7e16990e1","tid":2254037,"uid":175208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:07:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=4956261\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhome.gamer.com.tw%2FcreationDetail.php%3Fsn%3D4956261&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRM70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=469171b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://home.gamer.com.tw/creationDetail.php?sn=4956261</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">你的密碼會如何外洩？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n  想像一個情境：假設你今天在各大網站的帳號都使用這組看起來已經足夠複雜的強密碼「psFt*$4kM4Du&amp;F^6」。我們都知道，像這種在毫無規則的情況下以大寫英文、小寫英文、數字、特殊符號混合組成的密碼非常安全，因為根本不會被猜出來（光是大小寫英文加數字的 16 位密碼就有至少 4.7 &times; 10^28 種可能），一部經典電腦（一般的電腦）也難以在短時間用暴力破解的方式測試出你的密碼。<br />\n<br />\n  &mdash;&mdash;結果好死不死，這網站出包了，竟然讓偷偷入侵的駭客們得到了你的那組完整密碼。或許是網站管理員不慎把你未經過處理的完整密碼儲存在伺服器或資料庫裡（案 1），或許是服務提供者壓根就沒有幫你做好密碼傳輸過程的防護措施（案 2），或許是駭客透過軟體本身的漏洞控制整台伺服器、偷偷埋下後門在不知不覺的情況下監聽你的資訊（案 3）<br />\n(部分節錄)"},{"pid":"4b132d189a6ba9c3a6453c76ca0a08fd6191804b","tid":2254037,"uid":328061,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"一般使用者， <span class=\"orange\">唔好用同一組密碼</span><br />\n網站程序員，記得用 <span class=\"orange\">bcrypt</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">此post已完</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5aca60146643d15d8201f6aece3dc30333d6fa5","tid":2254037,"uid":175208,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b132d189a6ba9c3a6453c76ca0a08fd6191804b","tid":2254037,"uid":328061,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"一般使用者， <span class=\"orange\">唔好用同一組密碼</span><br />\n網站程序員，記得用 <span class=\"orange\">bcrypt</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">此post已完</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81998d92f991d7dbc5a6af00baa12734e0d6517d","tid":2254037,"uid":55597,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T02:56:16.000Z","msg":"最撚危險係儲存密碼<br />\n將 password 改做 text 睇得返<br />\n垃圾公司 木職員最鍾意 save password"},{"pid":"93f7cd51f2c11b733d86babc99c9955502719d76","tid":2254037,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T02:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最撚危險係儲存密碼<br />\n將 password 改做 text 睇得返<br />\n垃圾公司 d 職員最鍾意 save password</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4d63c4b97eebfa68983ea59d1bab19d3acb12a22","tid":2254037,"uid":5159,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T03:15:00.000Z","msg":"1. 每個網站使用獨立密碼<br />\n2. 可行既情況下開2FA<br />\n3. 裝防毒"},{"pid":"ed0918a420289dfe428e196e598a2a2ce79e69ac","tid":2254037,"uid":82365,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4d63c4b97eebfa68983ea59d1bab19d3acb12a22","tid":2254037,"uid":5159,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T03:15:00.000Z","msg":"1. 每個網站使用獨立密碼<br />\n2. 可行既情況下開2FA<br />\n3. 裝防毒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T04:55:06.000Z","msg":"個個網都獨立密碼既話 每次登入都要撳忘記密碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ecbc973dacb7a324a146e0dbb389bf7cd7485a3","tid":2254037,"uid":52972,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T04:59:33.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲有人鼓吹呢D ￥#FDh584 密碼， 根本人記唔到， 電腦容易撞。 當年提出個條契弟自己都已經認左衰， 反而仲有D低能網站用緊3000年前資訊<span class=\"red\">強制</span>用戶必須用呢類密碼。<br />\n<br />\n長度先係電腦既弱點。 最好就係加長密碼， 自己搵D句子， 又易記又難撞。"},{"pid":"1dc1d7a0104be2ff74bf65f3d7054f1f264b4043","tid":2254037,"uid":100412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"